Title: Coming of Rage
Plot: Grissom, Sarah, and Warrick investigate the murder of a teenager found on a construction site. Nick and Catherine try to discover how a woman on her lawn was killed by a gunshot  when no-one nearby had a gun.
ParentalRatingReason: Violence and horror scenes. Content may disturb
GuestStars: Brian Austin Green, Kimberlee Peterson, Jack Conley, Brian Sites, Chip Zien, Roxanne Beckford, Miranda Black, J. J. Dashnaw, Chris Fogleman, Justin Lanning, Connor Ross, Nicholas Roye, Basil Wallace, James DuMont
